# VL/VT deps are cloned + patched fresh inside the Docker builder stage. If
# the host happens to have stale `deps/VictoriaLogs/` or
# `lakehouse-traces/deps/{VictoriaLogs,VictoriaTraces}/` from a previous local
# build at a different commit, `COPY . .` would clobber the freshly-patched
# container state and the build fails with cryptic "undefined symbol" errors.
# CI checkouts don't have these dirs, so this only affects local docker builds.
deps/
lakehouse-traces/deps/

# Build outputs and ephemeral state.
dist/
bin/
/lakehouse-logs
/lakehouse-traces-bin
lakehouse-traces/lakehouse-traces
coverage.out
coverage.html
*.test
*.prof

# Local tooling state.
.git/
.github/
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo
